front.title: •Commander Praji
front.gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Devastator, also adds 1 to hyperspeed. Where present, cancels game text of C-3PO or R2-D2.
front.lore: Vader's aide on the Devastator. Personally supervised search for Death Star plans on Tatooine by Vader's order. Was graduated with honors from Imperial Navy Academy on Carida.

cancels: Game text of C-3PO or R2-D2
